posts.text: This is what I'll be dreaming about Monday night
The day after Trump was free of the Mueller report, he made the call to Zelensky that got him impeached. What will he do the day after he's acquitted of that impeachment?
The day after Trump was clear of the Mueller investigation, he made that call to Zelensky. What do you think Trump does the day after he's acquitted of an impeachment?
One of these days they're going to find out Kemp had ties to all these shenanigans. I know the House investigated him in March but there's been no progress. The guy's filthy corrupt.
This is so unclear and inscrutable, it may as well be an art project.
